# Markdown docs are the project trackers and get edited by tooling on Windows.
# Pinning them to LF stops a stray CRLF pass rewriting a 1900-line file as a
# whole-file diff, which is how PARTY.md once merged as 1956 insertions for a
# 156-line change -- unreviewable, and it re-churns on every later edit.
*.md text eol=lf
